  <CalDefinition Description="DAB_DisplayDABCategories cal defines whether the DAB category menu item (and associated DAB stations) should be displayed for DAB stations in a specific region. True means display a DAB category and any associated stations. False means do not display the DAB category as DAB stations cannot be accurately defined or should not be displayed for a given region. The default value is True. The tuner shall also monitor this cal and provide appropriate action to either support or not support the processing of this feature based on the cal setting. This helps balance and optimize system resources based on required features for a given market. When True, show DAB_DisplayDABCategories. When False, do not show DAB_DisplayDABCategories." Name="DAB_DisplayDABCategories" References="GIS-502" Usage="LOW,MID,HIGH,GEM,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU,VCU">
    <CalID>_Ea5MgTDdEeaCKJy9kX4aow</CalID>
