  <CalDefinition Description="DAB_Slide_Show_Menu_Item_On calibration defines the HMI menu item default state for DAB slide show images. When True, DAB slide show images are displayed. When False, DAB slide show images are not shown and the static default image is shown." Name="DAB_Slide_Show_Menu_Item_On" References="GIS-502" Usage="LOW,MID,HIGH,GEM,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU,VCU">
