  <CalDefinition Description="When enabled the user will no longer be able to launch direct tune. This item will appear grayed out and when selected the user will get the quick notice action unavailable while driving. Should user be in direct tune window when this calibration is enabled the user will be presented with the notification action unavailable while driving and when this notification is dismissed the user will be returned to the now playing screen." Name="DirectTuneLockout" References="GIS-502 6.4" Usage="LOW,MID,HIGH,GEM,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU,VCU">
