  <CalDefinition Description="When the MetadataCorrector calibration is set to TRUE, the MetadataCorrector_Menu_Item_On calibration shall be used to set the default state for the feature in the HMI menu. When TRUE, the metadata corrector function shall be active.  When FALSE, the metadata corrector function shall be inactive.  The default state for this cal is FALSE.  This cal is not valid if the MetadataCorrector cal is set to FALSE." Name="MetadataCorrector_Menu_Item_On" References="GIS-502 4.1.28.1, 4.1.28.2, 4.1.28.3" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,VCU">
    <CalID>_LvV2oblIEeSMLcx9-dghJQ</CalID>
